Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,, steadily: adv. 不断地\N They will hardly know which facts to select from the great mass of evidence that steadily accumulates.\N他们几乎不知道从稳步积累的大量证据中选择哪些事实。
