Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,, symbol: n.   符号, engrave: v.   雕刻, ivory: n.   象牙制品, mammoth: n.   （古）长毛象, tusk: n.   獠牙，长牙，象牙\N Lines and symbols which have been engraved on walls, bones, and the ivory tusks of mammoths.\N刻在墙壁，骨头和象牙象牙上的线条和符号。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,, nomad: n.   游牧民\N The nomads who made these markings lived by hunting and fishing during the last ice age which began.\N在开始的最后一个冰河时代，制作这些标记的游牧民族通过狩猎和钓鱼生活。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,, About 35,000 BC and ended about 10,000 BC by correlating markings made in various parts of the world.\N公元前约35,000，结束了约10,000公里，通过将世界各地的标记相关联。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,, phase: n.   月相，天相\N Historians have been able to read this difficult code. They have found that it is connected with the passage of days and the phases of the moon.\N历史学家能够阅读此困难的代码。他们发现它与几天的流逝和月球相关。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,, calendar: n.   历法，日历, primitive: adj. 原始的, depict: v.   描画，描绘\N It is, in fact, a primitive type of calendar. It has long been known that the hunting scenes depicted on walls were not simply a form of artistic.\N实际上，它是一种原始类型的日历。早就知道，墙上描绘的狩猎场景不仅仅是一种艺术形式。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,, Expression, they had a definite meaning. For they were as near as early man could get to writing.\N表达，它们具有明确的含义。因为他们和早期的人一样接近写作。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,, It is possible that there is a definite relation between these paintings and the markings that.\N这些绘画与标记之间可能存在明确的关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,, Sometimes accompany them. It seems that man was making a real effort to understand the seasons 20,000 years earlier than has.\N有时会陪伴他们。看来，男人正在努力地了解20，000年的季节。
